<br>
As Acorna stepped closer, her eyes widened and watched her closely.  Her skin twitched when Acorna felt her wound and she released a slight whince.  But as the Golden Hind healed her wound, she lowered her head and relaxed her ears, turning her head a bit more towards her.  She gently nudged Acorna's arm with her nose releasing a relaxed snort. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#993300>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#993300> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm94>Mythica Bestia Regum</a> <font color=#993300> - </font><a href="http://pub163.ezboard.com/bmythicalodysseyforum">Home</a><font color=#993300> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.3m<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

